measure.expression:
SELECT MAX(
        CASE
            WHEN {label/dt_timeline_timestamp.year} = "2018" THEN -123400,
            WHEN {label/dt_timeline_timestamp.year} = "2019" THEN 36200,
            WHEN {label/dt_timeline_timestamp.year} = "2020" THEN 54800,
            WHEN {label/dt_timeline_timestamp.year} = "2021" THEN 48100
        END,
        {dataset/f_timeline})
    WHERE {label/dt_timeline_timestamp.year} BETWEEN "2018" AND "2021"
measure.title: Sample XIRR
